test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:

 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7567fa6deec0> = [[1, -41], [1, -41, 1], [-41], [-41, 1], [1, -41], [1, -41, 1], ...].count
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert 41 == -41
 +  where 41 = <built-in function prod>([-1, -41])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
